This paper deals with the formalization of inductive data types and their combination with algebraic specification languages and strongly typed functional languages. This topic is relevant to several areas of computer science, including logic (cs.LO), programming languages (cs.PL), type theory (cs.TL), software engineering (cs.SE), and formal methods (cs.FL).
